Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.87,0:24:47.87,Spica - Signs,,0,0,0,,Tokyo National Space School\NSeagull Girls
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.54,0:24:53.62,Spica - Notes,,0,0,0,,Banners: Entrance Ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:32.00,Spica - Title,,0,0,0,,Test Complete
Comment: 0,0:13:01.96,0:13:11.97,Spica - Title,,0,0,0,,Eyecatch
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.98,0:24:35.98,Spica - Title,,0,0,0,,Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.00,0:25:00.01,Spica - Title,,0,0,0,,Space School Entrance Ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.88,0:01:53.92,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,My dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.92,0:01:56.67,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Year 1, Class 1, Kamogawa Asumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.42,0:02:01.68,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,My dream is to become a rocket driver!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.01,0:02:06.68,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,That's because I've heard that the Earth is very pretty when you look at it from space.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.68,0:02:11.19,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,So I want to become a rocket driver and go into space!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:15.19,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I want to take people to all sorts of different planets!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.11,0:02:19.20,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,And when they're on my rocket...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:23.70,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,...my dad and Lion-san will get special free rides!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.29,0:02:25.70,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,The end!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.68,0:02:45.97,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Damn it! This is the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.97,0:02:49.94,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It's going to be totally impossible to line all these up in these last two days!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.94,0:02:53.44,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,How many days do you think it took us to line these up in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:55.77,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Or so he says, Fuchuuya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.77,0:02:59.45,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Really, who do you think lined them up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.45,0:03:00.40,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Damn monk haircut boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.41,0:03:02.91,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,I don't want any more of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.91,0:03:05.08,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I've had more than enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.08,0:03:06.95,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I'm getting outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:09.46,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,We're just gonna fail no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.88,0:03:15.04,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, just hold on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.04,0:03:16.92,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Calm down a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.50,0:03:20.97,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Don't mess with me!\NHow can I be calm!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.18,0:03:25.38,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.38,0:03:27.68,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It's been bothering me for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:30.14,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,...but what do you think that is up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.23,0:03:33.52,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It's a surveillance camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.52,0:03:35.40,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,A surveillance camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.40,0:03:37.73,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What, you never noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.73,0:03:42.15,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,If you focus your eyes on it,\Nyou can see the inner lens moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:45.07,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,See? It just moved now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.79,0:03:49.12,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Which would mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:51.62,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,We were being watched this whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.62,0:03:52.83,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.83,0:03:54.33,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,For what reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:59.46,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,I see. We were all mistakenly letting ourselves focus on the dominoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:04.05,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,This was originally supposed to be a closed-environment adaptation test, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.05,0:04:10.02,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Right. The most important thing will be to finish out the seven days here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:12.27,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It's not about how many dominoes we line up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:13.27,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.27,0:04:14.93,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.93,0:04:16.56,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:20.23,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What reason would they have for shutting up three guys who don't know each other in a room like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.23,0:04:23.61,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,That's the thing that the school wants to see the most, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.61,0:04:26.74,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Say it so people can understand what you mean, Suzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.74,0:04:27.83,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I did...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.41,0:04:31.66,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,In other words, the thing you're lacking most.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.66,0:04:33.54,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.54,0:04:34.54,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.54,0:04:38.34,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Why are you always saying things that make people uncomfortable!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.34,0:04:40.05,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Who's doing that now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:41.01,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.09,0:04:46.72,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I thought of a wonderful way to finish lining up the dominoes in the last two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.72,0:04:48.60,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What? Seriously!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:54.14,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,It really is tiring having a moron in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.65,0:05:02.23,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,They must be observing everyone's progress from somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:07.28,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,Actually, I wonder how that other moron is doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:12.12,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Pull yourself together, Asumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:14.04,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Come on, Asumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.08,0:05:17.08,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,What's wrong!? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:33.68,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.23,0:05:36.73,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,Who's there...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.77,0:05:39.31,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,It's you, Lion-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.73,0:05:44.23,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,Lion-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.17,0:05:49.31,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,Why do you look so sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.28,0:05:52.98,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.99,0:05:56.45,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.66,0:06:02.91,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,Why is Yuigahama burning?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.66,0:06:12.93,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,Mom!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:20.15,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,She's calmed down a little bit now that she's lying down...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.15,0:06:22.90,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,...but it looks like she's not going to stop shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:26.19,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder what could have happened to Asumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.19,0:06:30.45,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Her mind is just in turmoil from the stress of this unfamiliar environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.99,0:06:32.62,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it's a temporary thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:34.62,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,That would be nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:37.58,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,She's been saying some weird things, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.04,0:06:41.17,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:43.09,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,You can tell by looking, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.09,0:06:45.84,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,We don't have any time to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.84,0:06:48.17,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,If you have time to be worrying about others...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.17,0:06:49.97,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,...you should line some up too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:53.60,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Really... Kamogawa-san is such a nuisance...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.60,0:06:56.89,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Panicking over a little thing like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:06:58.85,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,It's proof that her spirit is weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.94,0:07:06.69,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.07,0:07:09.15,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You know, Asumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.15,0:07:13.37,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,She said she wanted to be friends with you from the bottom of her heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.37,0:07:16.99,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,And you're more worried about {\i1}these{\i0} than someone like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:20.66,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Is that supposed to be one of the astronaut qualifications you talk about so much!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.30,0:07:32.22,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,Hey, Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.22,0:07:35.76,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,Why won't Mom come back home with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:53.70,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,Mom, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:55.53,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,It's me, Asumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.53,0:07:58.12,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,I'm always right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:02.79,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Hey, Asumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:04.79,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.79,0:08:05.75,Spica - Flashback,,0,0,0,,Wait right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.18,0:09:45.10,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, what do you think you're doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.64,0:09:48.35,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,I don't want any more of this... not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:53.40,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I really should have pressed this button sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.90,0:09:57.03,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,When Asumi is suffering so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.03,0:10:00.78,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I'm mad at myself for hesitating like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.74,0:10:07.71,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Passing the test while she's suffering like that...\NI wouldn't be happy about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.71,0:10:10.00,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I'd regret it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:13.13,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Because that just means I failed as a person!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.13,0:10:14.96,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Don't make it sound so pretty!{timing?}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.38,0:10:20.39,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You're just pushing your suffering onto Kamogawa-san, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.39,0:10:23.76,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You just want to run away and hide your weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:27.02,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You're worried about Kamogawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.02,0:10:28.48,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Don't make me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.48,0:10:30.44,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You're just a simple hypocrite!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.07,0:10:36.57,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, look. Resorting to violence again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.57,0:10:39.36,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,If you think you can change what people think like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:40.95,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,...you're quite mistaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.95,0:10:42.99,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,That's something that weak people do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.45,0:10:43.87,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.87,0:10:44.99,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:48.58,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Asumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:56.25,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I've always looked up at the sky, ever since I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:11:03.39,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I always, always, wanted to be closer to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.39,0:11:06.89,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,That's all that my dream is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.89,0:11:08.98,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,It's the only dream I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.89,0:11:14.44,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for worrying you, Kei-chan, Ukita-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.44,0:11:17.73,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,But I don't want to give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.73,0:11:20.28,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I want to try my best a little longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.28,0:11:25.66,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Ukita-san, Kei-chan, I want to try my best with both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:30.29,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I get it, Asumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.72,0:11:50.31,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Why don't you cool that off?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.81,0:11:54.35,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I hate your guts...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.35,0:11:56.48,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,...but I'll apologize for hitting you, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.86,0:12:00.40,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,The feeling's mutual. I never want to go through this again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.40,0:12:02.20,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What a brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.66,0:12:04.74,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Kei-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.70,0:12:07.99,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I know... We need to get this done, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.99,0:12:09.16,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:11.37,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,We don't have much time left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.37,0:12:14.88,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Still, we have no choice but to get as much done as we can, do we?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.83,0:12:16.84,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.25,0:12:21.17,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Even after lights out, the light in the bathroom still comes on, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:34.94,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,This is your wonderful idea!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:36.69,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.69,0:12:41.03,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,It's just pulling all-nighters lining up the dominoes with no breaks, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.03,0:12:42.28,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Well, sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.53,0:12:46.28,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Hey, the one who came up with this plan better not be sleeping!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.28,0:12:47.70,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:50.29,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Please be a little quieter!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.29,0:12:52.37,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Even without your yelling, everyone's on edge already!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.91,0:12:56.08,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I know that! Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.95,0:13:36.58,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I always thought these tasted chalky, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.25,0:13:40.63,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,They're convenient for situations like this, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.63,0:13:43.00,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,They make them just for that reason, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:45.88,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Well, that's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.51,0:13:48.84,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Asumi, it's your turn next.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:53.85,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Come on, Asumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.64,0:13:56.48,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.35,0:14:00.69,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,We're not getting any sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.69,0:14:03.23,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,...so we need to at least eat properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.15,0:14:06.57,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,How about your drink?\NIs orange juice okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:07.95,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.87,0:14:12.45,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.20,0:14:15.45,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Time to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.58,0:14:19.71,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Kei-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.58,0:14:22.46,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You're really good at cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.84,0:14:28.51,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.84,0:14:33.60,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I'm honored by your compliment!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.26,0:14:37.06,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Although it tastes the same no matter who makes it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:41.61,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:46.86,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Let's get these things lined up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.42,0:15:05.09,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I smell!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.42,0:15:10.80,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Me too...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.34,0:15:12.93,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Well, of course we do...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.93,0:15:18.81,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,We've been in this airtight room for two days without washing ourselves, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.81,0:15:20.56,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,No time to spare.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.56,0:15:21.19,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.65,0:15:23.65,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I haven't shampooed either!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.65,0:15:26.11,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I can't show myself like this to anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.11,0:15:29.65,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, I want to take a full shower and really wash my hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.65,0:15:33.57,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,You can shower as much as you want the day after we're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.32,0:15:37.74,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,However, I'm not sure whether you'll be crying or laughing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.54,0:15:41.92,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Right, right. I'm lining them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:43.46,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I just have to line them up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.75,0:15:45.75,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Gochisousama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.75,0:15:46.38,Spica - Notes,,0,0,0,,"Gochisousama" is a phrase said after meals.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.77,0:16:02.73,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Just one more day of this, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.73,0:16:03.65,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.99,0:16:19.91,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,Just one more day until the exam is over...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.91,0:16:21.33,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,Just one more day!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.35,0:16:43.10,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Just two rooms, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.86,0:16:53.40,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,So thirteen teams lasted until the final day, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.40,0:16:55.95,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,That's more than we expected, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:16:57.07,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,I guess it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.07,0:16:59.41,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,But that project must have been impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:00.99,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,The dominoes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.99,0:17:03.16,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder who thought that one up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.16,0:17:06.71,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I would have pressed the emergency button on the first day!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.71,0:17:08.17,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I feel the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.26,0:17:14.67,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, check this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.67,0:17:15.88,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.88,0:17:18.55,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.39,0:17:26.56,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Some of the rooms got all of them lined up!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.56,0:17:27.56,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.56,0:17:30.44,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,0350 and 2960 did.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.95,0:17:40.74,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:43.95,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Now I can finally take a shower...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.59,0:17:56.67,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You know, Asumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.67,0:18:00.72,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,She said she wanted to be friends with you from the bottom of her heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.27,0:18:05.73,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,There's no way she could be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.23,0:18:10.15,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,No one can understand me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.90,0:18:17.24,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,So if you think of this "river of heaven" as a real river...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.90,0:18:17.24,Spica - Notes,,0,0,0,,The Japanese term for the Milky Way galaxy is "river of heaven"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.24,0:18:23.49,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,...each individual little star can be thought of as bits of sand or g...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.33,0:18:25.25,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Gravel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:29.46,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,...gravel in that whole. This is again part of...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.46,0:18:33.96,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,As long as can I remember, since I was a very small child,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.96,0:18:36.80,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,I almost never set foot outside of that room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:42.01,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,If I tried to leave the room, I would be severely scolded.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.39,0:18:49.81,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,The tutors who always came at the same time...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.48,0:18:54.69,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,The three meals a day that always came at the same time...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.69,0:18:57.32,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,The meals I spent alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.44,0:19:00.70,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,That forever unchanging life...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.66,0:19:03.32,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,In that unchanging room...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.33,0:19:05.45,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.87,0:19:10.71,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,The stars I could see from that window so high up were the only...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.71,0:19:12.67,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,The stars were the only...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.67,0:19:15.21,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,The only thing that changed a bit, day by day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.55,0:19:18.21,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,I, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.30,0:19:23.68,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,I, too, was always looking up at the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.97,0:19:27.47,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,She doesn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.47,0:19:29.23,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,There's no way anyone could understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.30,0:19:58.55,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Mom, look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.55,0:20:00.26,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I passed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.26,0:20:02.13,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Now, one day, I'll be able to go into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.97,0:20:06.26,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,I'll make sure to show you how I can\Nbecome a rocket driver, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.16,0:20:25.57,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Kamogawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.16,0:20:29.12,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Suzunari-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.45,0:20:34.75,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Really? So you passed the exam! Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.75,0:20:36.54,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.63,0:20:38.96,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You're not happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.96,0:20:41.97,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I'm happy. Very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.97,0:20:42.72,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.09,0:20:47.26,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,When I think about things... and my father...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.26,0:20:51.31,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I start to wonder if it's really okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.06,0:20:53.89,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What do you think, sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.89,0:20:56.73,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,About my desire to go into space...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.73,0:20:58.61,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What do you really think?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.40,0:21:02.57,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.32,0:21:05.24,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,The answer to that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.24,0:21:06.41,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,...is right here, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.66,0:21:08.57,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.58,0:21:13.12,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,No matter what the people around you think...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.12,0:21:16.08,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,...you have to believe in your own dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.13,0:21:21.96,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure many people will say many different things to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.96,0:21:25.01,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,And there may be times when you feel discouraged.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.01,0:21:27.72,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,When that happens, the answer is always right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.30,0:21:30.26,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,It's nowhere else but there inside of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.90,0:21:41.44,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.57,0:21:43.28,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Kamogawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.28,0:21:46.11,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,My dad hasn't seen this yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.66,0:21:57.21,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, little one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.43,0:22:17.10,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,So these are the successful applicants' papers?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.31,0:22:25.82,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,So they'll be the first class of this new astronaut training course, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.82,0:22:30.62,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,That's right. They'll be your students starting next semester, Sano-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.62,0:22:34.08,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,There sure are a lot of different kids!\NI'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.45,0:22:37.58,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Though saying that, I'll still only be their lecturer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.58,0:22:40.83,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I probably won't get too deeply involved with them...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.17,0:22:45.96,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Is there someone you know in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.96,0:22:49.43,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What? No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.80,0:22:54.01,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Kamogawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.98,0:24:36.98,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I've said goodbye to Lion-san and begun my new life at the girls' dorm in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.70,0:24:45.20,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Of course I have Kei-chan and Ukita-san with me at school!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.20,0:24:47.87,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,And Fuchuuya-kun passed as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.87,0:24:52.62,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,But I'm feeling just a bit lonely in the nooks and crannies of my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.62,0:24:56.88,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Next time on Twin Spica:\NSpace School Entrance Ceremony.